        "end": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "魏州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_029_000034",
    "sentence": "驗其文，即「受命於天，子孫寶之」八字也，群僚稱賀。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_029_000035",
    "sentence": "傳真師於廣明中，遇京師喪亂得之，秘藏已四十年矣。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "明",
        "label": "ORG",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "四十年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 19,
        "end": 22
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_029_000036",
    "sentence": "篆文古體，人不之識，至是獻之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_029_000037",
    "sentence": "時淮南楊溥、四川王衍皆遣使致書，勸帝嗣唐帝位，帝不從。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_029_000038",
    "sentence": "二月，代州刺史王建及卒。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "代州",
        "label": "LOC",
